  "content": "<h2>关于我</h2><ul><li data-pid=\"Slcs4v3D\">  I&#39;m a graduate CS major at Harbin Institute of Technology, Shenzhen.</li><li data-pid=\"IKAPJPJY\">  I&#39;m currently working as a research engineer in <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.maimemo.com/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Maimemo Inc</a>.</li><li data-pid=\"T3seCXRS\">  I&#39;m developing algorithm of <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spaced_repetition\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">spaced repetition</a> and simulator of human memory.</li><li data-pid=\"YpYaBQ5D\">  I&#39;m the founder of <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thoughts Memo</a>, a translation group that spreads educational technology.</li><li data-pid=\"ZA4zEKHg\">  Ask me about <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//apps.ankiweb.net/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Anki</a> or <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//super-memory.com/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">SuperMemo</a>, I&#39;m a diehard <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flashcard\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">flashcard</a> fan!</li><li data-pid=\"HAaGldMg\">  My personal <a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/column/c_1280249768422608896\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">column</a> is at ZhiHu.</li><li data-pid=\"2eSZhs6n\">  How to reach me: <a href=\"mailto:jarrett.ye@outlook.com\">jarrett.ye@outlook.com</a></li></ul><h2>阅读指南</h2><h3>个人随笔</h3><p data-pid=\"0qmuEuli\">平时写的一些个人思考，都发布在此：</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/column/c_1280249768422608896\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-52a669542a8699d42a3c5796c7e536e9_l.jpg\" data-image-width=\"200\" data-image-height=\"200\" class=\"internal\">学委叶哥的随笔</a><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><h3>SuperMemo</h3><h3>渐进阅读</h3><p data-pid=\"BcPpUKjb\">目前我的主力学习工具就是 SuperMemo，想要了解如何使用 SuperMemo 进行高效学习实践，可阅读：</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/column/c_1308886122672484352\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-52a669542a8699d42a3c5796c7e536e9_l.jpg\" data-image-width=\"200\" data-image-height=\"200\" class=\"internal\">SuperMemo—渐进学习最前沿！</a><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><h3>认知基石</h3><p data-pid=\"Czts1jZS\">SuperMemo 的作者对学习进行三十多年的研究，许多学习知识的相关译文已经收录于此：</p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/column/c_1525846506753658880\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\"internal\">认知基石 &amp; 学校教育</a><h3>学校教育</h3><p data-pid=\"Yf59X9Rw\">Piotr Wozniak 博士有许多批判学校教育的文章，里面有不少暴论，也有不少洞见，建议还在苦苦挣扎的同学们阅读：</p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/column/supermemo-guru-cn\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-52a669542a8699d42a3c5796c7e536e9_l.jpg\" data-image-width=\"200\" data-image-height=\"200\" class=\"internal\">学校教育</a><h3>间隔重复</h3><p data-pid=\"DYkYTl-X\">间隔重复是 Anki、SuperMemo 等软件的核心算法，本专栏收录了间隔重复的历史，以及间隔重复的相关理论，有志深入研究人类记忆的朋友可以阅读：</p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/column/c_1525782291741208576\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-52a669542a8699d42a3c5796c7e536e9_l.jpg\" data-image-width=\"200\" data-image-height=\"200\" class=\"internal\">间隔重复 &amp; 注意力管理</a><h3>Anki 高考</h3><p data-pid=\"pZ_6HJw5\">我在知乎建立的第一个专栏，记录了我与 Anki 并肩作战，一起对抗高考的日子。</p><p data-pid=\"35hgQLKn\">大部分关于 Anki 入门的教程都收录于此：</p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/column/ankigaokao\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-915dfc2907d61311962269fc24181b74_l.jpg\" data-image-width=\"419\" data-image-height=\"419\" class=\"internal\">AnkiX高考</a><h3>经验</h3><p data-pid=\"v-25z7aP\">收录了我自己和几位一同使用 Anki 备战高考的同学的备考经验，对 Ankier 来说，这才是最宝贵的教程：</p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/collection/814079168\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\"internal\">Anki 高考经验</a><h3>技巧</h3><p data-pid=\"Nrajz1to\">这里有很多关于 Anki 的奇淫技巧，请有选择性地阅读：</p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/collection/814089332\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\"internal\">Anki 高考技巧</a><h3>牌组</h3><p data-pid=\"a-Nos9M5\">我和一些同学做的 Anki 牌组，可能有上万张，仅供参考：</p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/collection/487368329\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\"internal\">Anki 牌组分享</a><h3>其它</h3><p data-pid=\"xs0cFnYx\">用过一段时间常青笔记，它把间隔重复和双链结合得不错，可以了解一下：</p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/column/c_1525779661229830144\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-52a669542a8699d42a3c5796c7e536e9_l.jpg\" data-image-width=\"200\" data-image-height=\"200\" class=\"internal\">常青笔记 &amp; 知识工作</a><h2>咨询指北</h2><p data-pid=\"qcTMIEn6\">咨询前请务必阅读：</p><p data-pid=\"n8x5OA9E\"><b><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//github.com/ryanhanwu/How-To-Ask-Questions-The-Smart-Way/blob/main/README-zh_CN.md%23%E6%8F%90%E9%97%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">《提问的智慧》</a></b></p><p data-pid=\"je7robuR\">我关闭了陌生人私信和付费咨询，任何问题请在评论区交流，或者在知乎上提问并 <a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/4c592f496dc33822b560b382907ff1d0\" data-hash=\"4c592f496dc33822b560b382907ff1d0\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$4c592f496dc33822b560b382907ff1d0\">@叶峻峣</a>。</p><p data-pid=\"7iGTYAA0\">不接受以下类型的问题：</p><ul><li data-pid=\"TaeHtC4F\">可通过卸载知乎解决的问题（如高考还剩xx天，目前成绩xxx，怎么逆袭）</li><li data-pid=\"bg8V0kMB\">涉及个人隐私的问题</li><li data-pid=\"WnrMdUWn\">不涉及我写作领域的问题</li><li data-pid=\"eD7XbaA9\">已经在评论区回复过的相似问题</li></ul><p data-pid=\"qRHYKG-n\">觉得我的文章和回答对你有帮助的话，欢迎赞赏~</p>",
